<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT-Lilly Industries upgraded.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT-Lilly Industries upgraded.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Hilliard Lyons analyst Stephen O'Neil said he raised his rating on Lilly Industries Inc to buy from hold.</p>
<p>-- Shares in the maker of industrial coatings and specialty chemicals closed Monday on the New York Stock Exchange at 18-1/8.</p>
<p>-- &quot;A healthy U.S. economy usually bodes well for Lilly's business, the company sustains attractive returns due to the value added nature of its products, the Guardsman acquisition provides a visible source of earnings growth and margins have expanded as raw material cost pressures have moderated,&quot; O'Neil said.</p>
<p>((--Chicago Newsdesk 312-408-8787))</p>
